# Catalog and Admin

Checklist for new catalog entities:

1. Migration table with `slug`, `name`, `source`, `data JSONB`
2. Zod schema in `src/lib/schemas/`
3. PHB fallback TS in `src/lib/dnd/phb/` if applicable
4. Server CRUD in `catalog.ts` (`"use server"`) + client reads in `catalog-client.ts`
5. Admin manager under `src/app/admin/` + entry in `admin/database/page.tsx` CATEGORIES
6. Merge tests in `catalog-merge.test.ts` or new colocated test

Slug is the stable ID; upsert with `onConflict: "slug"`.
